solutions.name: 一只书虫仔
solutions.slogan: 你将对着以绝望为名的希望微笑 自我责任 因果报应 责任转嫁 罪责难逃 梦如泡沫 祸福相依 物极必反 言多必失 死人无口 逝者安息

solutions.name: AsunderSquall
solutions.slogan: The cruelest fate is to have hope and see it crushed before your eyes.

solutions.name: Fatalis_Lights
solutions.slogan: 『 Even so, we met after it all. We were able to smile again. 』
